high_descs: go to your left around the island
pick up the small butter knife near the silver plate
go to the other side of the island where the apple and bread are sitting
slice the apple with the knife
turn around and stop at the white trash can
put the butter knife into the trash can
go back to the island to the apple and bread
pick up a slice of the apple
go around the island to the microwave on the counter above the dishwasher
place the apple slice in the microwave and cook it, remove the apple from the microwave
take the cooked apple slice to the white trash can where you threw away the knife
throw the apple slice into the trash can
anns.task_desc: Throw away a knife and a cooked slice of apple

high_descs: Go to stand between the kitchen sink and the island, then turn right and face the island.
Pick up the butter knife from the left of the silver plate.
Bring the butter knife around to the other side of the kitchen island, then turn left and face the island.
Cut the apple on the kitchen island with the knife.
Bring the knife to the white trash can behind you.
Throw the knife in the trash can.
Go back to the island and face the sliced apple.
Pick up an apple slice from the island.
Bring the apple slice over to the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave and cook it, then take it out again.
Bring the cooked apple slice over to the white trash can.
Throw the apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a piece of cooked apple.

high_descs: turn left moving forward and turn right at the counter stopping at the right end of the counter where the knives are sitting
turn to face the counter and pick up the silver knife to the left of the plate
turn right and then turn left at the end of the counter, go around to the other side of the counter, stopping at the center and turn left to face the green apple
move forward to be in front of the apple
slice the apple with the knife, turn around and move to the trash can on the left
put the knife in to the trash can
turn to the left and move back to face the counter with the apple slice
pick up the small slice of apple
turn right, move to the end of the counter and turn left moving towards the microwave and the counter next to the toaster
open the microwave door, put the apple in to the microwave in front of the egg, close the door and cook the apple for a few seconds, open the door and remove the apple slice
turn around and move forward to the end of the center kitchen island and turn right at the end of that counter, move forward passed the fridge stopping to face the grey trash can on the left
put the apple slice in to the trash can
anns.task_desc: put a knife and cooked apple slice into the trash can
